nodes.body: Coming here from PR triage: can you comment on the status of this PR? Is this an experiment, basically not intended to land, or would you like this to get reviewed? In the latter case, please merge master. Thanks!

I think that there should be more auto-generation of results such as the ones in this PR, but this was an early experiment and probably one that was too ambitious.  I have made simpler experiments that were successful, and I plan to think more about this.

For the moment, this does not need reviewing and I'm labelling as awaiting-author.
